326
00:17:25,145 --> 00:17:27,314
Thank you.


327
00:17:36,756 --> 00:17:38,291
Ah.

328
00:17:43,296 --> 00:17:44,231
Hmm.


331
00:18:09,789 --> 00:18:11,124
Buon giorno, Signora  

