Signora,
where you go?

406
00:21:34,461 --> 00:21:35,395
Sorry?

407
00:21:35,428 --> 00:21:36,829
Are you lost?

408
00:21:37,029 --> 00:21:39,332
We missed the boat.
My fault.

409
00:21:39,366 --> 00:21:42,369
It's a long way to walk.
I give you a ride.

410
00:21:42,402 --> 00:21:43,470
Well, I--
I don't know.

411
00:21:43,503 --> 00:21:46,339
Your husband
can come with me!

