00:25:48,981 --> 00:25:49,882
for this,
that, and the other.

486
00:25:49,916 --> 00:25:52,619
We would've asked you
to join us, of course,

487
00:25:52,652 --> 00:25:54,253
but you weren't
at breakfast.

488
00:25:54,286 --> 00:25:57,089
I overslept,
