504
00:26:28,721 --> 00:26:31,057
Would that it were.

505
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:33,960
I tell you what, though.
As a peace offering,

506
00:26:33,993 --> 00:26:35,928
would you do me
the great honor

507
00:26:35,962 --> 00:26:36,829
