tonight?

508
00:26:36,863 --> 00:26:41,267
Oh, thank you. Yes,
that would be lovely.

509
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:42,802
Good.

510
00:26:42,835 --> 00:26:44,103
7:30?

511
00:26:44,136 --> 00:26:46,138
Uh...heh.

512
00:26:47,039 --> 00:26:51,644
I don't often make
the same mistake twice.

               





