00:31:46,038 --> 00:31:48,040
Better not miss your train!

590
00:31:48,074 --> 00:31:50,042
No.


592
00:32:11,563 --> 00:32:14,100
Arrivederci!


 
594
00:32:18,037 --> 00:32:20,039
That was a cruel
thing to do.

595
00:32:20,072 --> 00:32:22,608
What do you mean? He went
